reviewText: I ordered it becasue my friend Howie Gold was on the video.  Cool video even if Howie only came in 2nd place

I bought the videocassette, which was on sale, many years ago. In this standup comedy competition, 3 aspiring comedians compete, their sets interspersed with jokes from young Jay Leno's routine. It is interesting to compare the brazen Jay Leno of yesteryear with his polished routines of today. Check out the winner's biography on Wikipedia to see how he has made his way in show business over the years. I've been looking for the DVD for quite some time, and was very happy to see it finally available.
